lock-heading\">🛒 Buying + Care Guide: How to Choose &amp; Maintain Indoor Plants</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Feature</th><th>Why It Matters</th><th>Tip</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Pot &amp; Drainage</td><td>Many décor pots lack drainage, which can kill roots</td><td>Use liner pots or only water lightly</td></tr><tr><td>Light Conditions</td><td>Some plants (polka dot, mini) need moderate light; others tolerate low light</td><td>Scout sun exposure before ordering</td></tr><tr><td>Watering</td><td>Overwatering is the top killer</td><td>Let soil dry slightly before watering</td></tr><tr><td>Humidity &amp; Temperature</td><td>Dry indoor air or drafts can stress plants</td><td>Mist leaves or group plants to raise humidity</td></tr><tr><td>Repotting</td><td>Plants eventually outgrow small nursery pots</td><td>Use fresh potting mix and replant to next size</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">✅ Final Thoughts &amp; Recommendations</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Want a <strong>safe all-rounder</strong>? The <strong>Costa Farms 3-Pack</strong> is a solid buy.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Crave <strong>color and variation</strong>? Go with <strong>Polka Dot Plant Collection</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Prefer a <strong>multipack that grows</strong>? Choose <strong>Live Mini Pack</strong> or <strong>Altman 12PK</strong>.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>For a <strong>starter mix with reliable varieties</strong>, the <strong>Essential Houseplant pack</strong> is ideal.</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Let me know if you want me to supply the HTML version (with meta tags, alt attributes, schema markup) so you can paste straight into WordPress!</p>\n"
